═══════════════════════════════════════════
API INTEGRATION ANNOTATIONS
═══════════════════════════════════════════

On each screen that triggers an API call, add a developer annotation layer (using Figma's annotation tools or a sticky note component) showing:

Screen 2 (Flo connection): 
→ Flo OAuth 2.0: GET partners.flo.health/oauth/authorize
→ On callback: POST /oauth/token to exchange code for access_token
→ Store token: Expo SecureStore (encrypted, device-only)

Screen 5 (Home — workout card):
→ getWorkoutRecommendation() in src/services/gemma.ts
→ Params: { phase, cycleDay, energyRating, recentWorkouts, goals }
→ Returns: WorkoutRecommendation JSON
→ Model: gemma-4-it (API) or gemma-4-e4b (on-device LiteRT)

Screen 7-8 (Log):
→ parseWorkoutLog() in src/services/gemma.ts
→ Params: { logText, phase, cycleDay }
→ Returns: { energyRating, completionPercent, mood, adjustment }

Screen 5 (Flo sync indicator):
→ GET https://api.flo.health/v1/cycle/current
→ Auth: Bearer {access_token}
→ Returns: { start_date, predicted_length, current_day, phase }

═══════════════════════════════════════════
EXPORT NOTES
═══════════════════════════════════════════

• Export all components for React Native (Expo) — use auto-layout so they translate cleanly
• Use 8pt grid throughout
• All spacing: multiples of 4px (4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32, 48)
• Corner radius: 8px (small), 12px (medium), 16px (large), 100px (pill)
• All touch targets: minimum 44×44px
• Ensure all text contrast meets WCAG AA (4.5:1 minimum)
• Export icons as SVG for React Native use